    "# Tech Note - Sine Sweep"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "891e7c44",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "周波数を経時変化させる\n",
    "\n",
    "* $f(t)$ [Hz]：時刻$t$での周波数\n",
    "* $f_{start}$ [Hz]：掃引開始周波数\n",
    "* $f_{end}$ [Hz]：掃引終了周波数\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "f(t) = f_{start} \\cdot \\left( \\frac{f_{end}}{f_{start}} \\right)^{\\frac{t}{T}} \\quad \\quad (1)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
